OL,3,CMore than 100 children caught with
OL,4,Cknives in South Yorkshire schools in 3
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FMore than 100 children have been
OL,8,Fcaught taking knives into schools in
OL,9,FSouth Yorkshire over the last three
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FThe figures show the number of young
OL,13,Fpeople under the age of 18 reported to
OL,14,Fthe police for taking knives into
OL,15,Fschools between 2022 to 2024, across
OL,16,FBarnsley, Doncaster, Rotherham, and
OL,17,FSheffield.
