OL,3,CMore than 100 children caught with
OL,4,Cknives in South Yorkshire schools in 3
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FSouth Yorkshire Police revealed that
OL,8,FSheffield saw the highest number of
OL,9,Fincidents, recording 37 between 2022
OL,10,Fand 2024.
OL,12,FIn the same period, Doncaster saw 30
OL,13,Fincidents, Rotherham 22 and Barnsley
OL,14,F14.
OL,16,FOnly three per cent of cases resulted
OL,17,Fin formal legal action like charges or
OL,18,Fsummons. The majority of cases
OL,19,Finvolved alternative actions, such as
OL,20,Fcautions, community resolutions, or
OL,21,Fdiversionary interventions.
