OL,3,CMore than 100 children caught with
OL,4,Cknives in South Yorkshire schools in 3
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FThe latest figures come just weeks
OL,8,Fafter 15-year-old Harvey Willgoose was
OL,9,Fstabbed to death at school in
OL,10,FSheffield.
OL,12,FSuperintendent David Cowley, South
OL,13,FYorkshire Police's force lead for
OL,14,Fknife crime, said: "We are dedicated
OL,15,Fto combating knife crime in South
OL,16,FYorkshire - and take a robust approach
OL,17,Fin response to incidents and those
OL,18,Ffound to be carrying a weapon.
