OL,7,F"We have seen the devastation it
OL,8,Fcauses to our local communities, and
OL,9,Fare committed to working with
OL,10,Fpartners, including local authorities
OL,11,Fand the South Yorkshire Violence
OL,12,FReduction Unit, taking an evidence-
OL,13,Fbased approach to prevent and reduce
OL,14,Fknife crime.
