OL,3,CMore than 100 children caught with
OL,4,Cknives in South Yorkshire schools in 3
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,F"This includes engagement work with
OL,8,Flocal schools and youth groups where,
OL,9,Fthrough our Knives Take Lives
OL,10,Fcampaign, tailored educational talks
OL,11,Fand events which are delivered to make
OL,12,Fyoung people aware of the dangers of
OL,13,Fcarrying a knife."
OL,15,FAs part of efforts to tackle knife
OL,16,Fcrime, South Yorkshire Police are
OL,17,Frunning educational campaigns aimed at
OL,18,Fyoung people in schools and youth
OL,19,Fgroups. These events focus on raising
OL,20,Fawareness about the dangers of
OL,21,Fcarrying a knife.
